{"tid":1846290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曱近平呢個時候只識講八股空叫口號","createTime":"2020-01-27T14:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T07:19:52.000Z","uid":156363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"000385fa81348a2f063ee27b708438d74181f956","tid":1846290,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"中共總書記習近平作出重要指示，強調在當前防控新型肺炎的嚴峻鬥爭中，各級黨組織及廣大黨員幹部，必須牢記人民利益高於一切，不忘初心、牢記使命，團結帶領廣大人民，堅決貫徹落實黨中央決策部署。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，各級黨委要科學判斷形勢、精準把握疫情，統一領導、指揮、行動，領導班子與領導幹部要堅守崗位、靠前指揮，做到守土有責、擔責、盡責。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，要激勵引導廣大黨員幹部，在危難時刻挺身而出、英勇奮鬥、紮實工作，經得住考驗，緊緊依靠人民，堅決打贏疫情防控阻擊戰。"},{"pid":"b9593ebc4e339302741115cad000d90775b120d8","tid":1846290,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"講完等於冇講，不如換個識既黎做啦。"},{"pid":"388a8683306965b0f90ed874a6be4d2c8108d972","tid":1846290,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a3daaa1834aa4e0db3661d74e6be0bbe098e084","tid":1846290,"uid":237237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"指示左乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf810d00228479ca7da76c2eea3af26fa984ce0","tid":1846290,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢醒我先驚<br />\n<br />\n咁就啱啱好"},{"pid":"82b73c692fa9cd68c027cc07cc074cd5551ffe34","tid":1846290,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf810d00228479ca7da76c2eea3af26fa984ce0","tid":1846290,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢醒我先驚<br />\n<br />\n咁就啱啱好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"col